Package: gglayer
Title: Extra Layers for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: c(person(given="Guangchuang", family="Yu", email = "guangchuangyu@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person(given="Shipeng", family ="Guo", role="ctb")
           )
Description: Implements several extra layers for the 'ggplot2' graphic system, 
  including geom_cake() (uses birthday cake as symbolic point), geom_triangle() (uses triangle as symbolic point), 
  geom_segment_c() (allows continuous color mapping for line segment) and 
  geom_ord_ellipse() (adds confidence ellipse to ordinary plot produced by ggord()).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
	dplyr,
  grDevices,
  ggplot2,
	grid,
  magrittr,
  plyr,
  utils
Suggests:
  rvcheck
